@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@scriptId = script20260406000000000000

### 生成音频（把 @scriptId 替换成 generateScript 返回值）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lesson/generateAudio
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scriptId": "{{scriptId}}",
  "voiceType": "female_standard",
  "audioFormat": "mp3",
  "sectionIds": ["sec001", "sec002"],
  "enc": "demo-signature"
}
